Sentencas: The performance of a single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell was studied using a ceria-based solid electrolyte at temperatures below 773 kelvin.
Titulo: A low-operating-temperature solid oxide fuel cell in hydrocarbon-air mixtures

Sentencas: Electromotive forces of similar to 900 millivolts were generated from the cell in a flowing mixture of ethane or propane and air, where the solid electrolyte functioned as a purely ionic conductor.
Titulo: A low-operating-temperature solid oxide fuel cell in hydrocarbon-air mixtures

Sentencas: The electrode-reaction resistance was negligibly small in the total internal resistances of the cell.
Titulo: A low-operating-temperature solid oxide fuel cell in hydrocarbon-air mixtures

Sentencas: The resulting peak power density reached 403 and 101 milliwatts per square centimeter at 773 and 623 kelvin, respectively.
Titulo: A low-operating-temperature solid oxide fuel cell in hydrocarbon-air mixtures
